HMSh'a 'aShUr ChZH ChBQVQ HNBY'a.
'yD-'aNH YHVH ShV'yThY VL'a ThShM'y 'aZ'yQ 'aLYK ChMS VL'a ThVShY'y.
LMH ThUr'aNY 'aVN V'yML ThBYT VShD VChMS LNGDY VYHY UrYB VMDVN YSh'a.
'yL-KN ThPhVG ThVUrH VL'a-YTSh'a LNTShCh MShPhT KY UrSh'y MKThYUr 'aTh-HTShDYQ 'yL-KN YTSh'a MShPhT M'yQL.
Ur'aV BGVYM VHBYTV VHThMHV ThMHV KY-Ph'yL Ph'yL BYMYKM L'a Th'aMYNV KY YSPhUr.
KY-HNNY MQYM 'aTh-HKShDYM HGVY HMUr VHNMHUr HHVLK LMUrChBY-'aUrTSh LUrShTh MShKNVTh L'a-LV.
'aYM VNVUr'a HV'a MMNV MShPhTV VSh'aThV YTSh'a.
VQLV MNMUrYM SVSYV VChDV MZ'aBY 'yUrB VPhShV PhUrShYV VPhUrShYV MUrChVQ YB'aV Y'yPhV KNShUr ChSh L'aKVL.
KLH LChMS YBV'a MGMTh PhNYHM QDYMH VY'aSPh KChVL ShBY.
VHV'a BMLKYM YThQLS VUrZNYM MShChQ LV HV'a LKL-MBTShUr YShChQ VYTShBUr 'yPhUr VYLKDH.
'aZ ChLPh UrVCh VY'yBUr V'aShM ZV KChV L'aLHV.
HLV'a 'aThH MQDM YHVH 'aLHY QDShY L'a NMVTh YHVH LMShPhT ShMThV VTShVUr LHVKYCh YSDThV.
THVUr 'yYNYM MUr'aVTh Ur'y VHBYT 'aL-'yML L'a ThVKL LMH ThBYT BVGDYM ThChUrYSh BBL'y UrSh'y TShDYQ MMNV.
VTh'yShH 'aDM KDGY HYM KUrMSh L'a-MShL BV.
KLH BChKH H'yLH YGUrHV BChUrMV VY'aSPhHV BMKMUrThV 'yL-KN YShMCh VYGYL.
'yL-KN YZBCh LChUrMV VYQTUr LMKMUrThV KY BHMH ShMN ChLQV VM'aKLV BUr'aH.
H'yL KN YUrYQ ChUrMV VThMYD LHUrG GVYM L'a YChMVL.
